Package: pluscoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Pluscoin is a crypto-currency project forked from both Bitcoin and peercoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original Bitcoin's
 preferable properties.
 .
 This package provides peercoind, a daemon client for the Peercoin network.

Package: pluscoin-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Pluscoin is a crypto-currency project forked from Bitcoin with aim to achieve
 energy-efficiency and keep as much as possible the original Bitcoin's
 preferable properties.
 .
This package provides Pluscoin-Qt, a GUI client for Pluscoin based on Qt.